Package: deltafish
Title: Accesses an Integrated Fish Count and Length Dataset from the San Francisco Delta
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Jeanette",
           family = "Clark",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jclark@nceas.ucsb.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4703-1974")),
    person(given = "Sam",
           family = "Bashevkin",
